      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 9,
      "message": "This is not related to 3.2 version. Actually it could be done earlier. Docker compose by default creates network in which every container can access others by service name:\n\nhttps://docs.docker.com/compose/networking/\n\n`link` in case of compose gives us network-alias which is unnecessary (because I override MYSQL_HOST env). Also `link` option is consider legacy.",
